20:25.024 --> 20:26.126
They're irrevocable.

20:26.987 --> 20:40.165
By the way, even though that verse is often quoted to assure believers of the faithfulness of God in gift giving, never forget or overlook the fact that Paul was speaking primarily of Israel's call by God that it is irrevocable.

20:40.665 --> 20:43.329
He will fulfill every promise he's ever made to Israel.

20:43.809 --> 20:44.210
Amen.

20:45.378 --> 20:48.021
