In 1 Corinthians 12 verses 4 to 7 Paul explained that there are distinctive varieties of gifts and they vary but the Holy Spirit remains the same and he said there are distinctive varieties of service but it's the same Lord who was served and there are distinctive varieties of operation to accomplish things for God

