demonstrating division and understanding in the body of Messiah.

25:06.138 --> 25:16.894
The other day I heard a strong true believer nevertheless be moaning the fact that some believers he said face today's problems by only wanting to escape in the rapture rather than working for revival.

25:17.635 --> 25:22.142
My answer is that we must work for revival while also watching for the rapture.

25:22.943 --> 25:31.836
It's not an either or situation but we must be doing both occupying and working until Jesus comes and faithfully watching for him to come.

25:32.597 --> 25:33.138
Remember

25:33.282 --> 25:41.194
Once we're saved, God doesn't give every Christian the same spiritual gifts, opportunities, responsibilities, or measure of enabling grace for service.

25:41.774 --> 25:46.301
All believers have our place on the wall and our individual assignments from the Lord.

25:46.882 --> 25:51.048
The Lord gives each one of us according to our God given assignments on the wall.

25:51.729 --> 25:53.812
Some believers have been inspired to be a watchman.

25:54.613 --> 26:00.562
I applaud consistent watching for the Lord while never falling into the trap of date setting.

26:01.122 --> 26:03.605
No one knows the day or hour of the Lord's return.

26:04.066 --> 26:09.873
However, a convergence of biblical signs and timelines suggests that His coming is near.

26:10.614 --> 26:12.797
We live in prophetic end times.

26:13.277 --> 26:16.982
When people are surprised or angry, they shout the name of the Lord Jesus.

26:17.463 --> 26:21.147
Why don't they take Buddhas or Muhammad's name in vain?

26:21.668 --> 26:24.612
But devil's blaspheme true deity.

26:25.192 --> 26:29.778
Artificial intelligence is bringing about such deception that soon on the internet,

26:30.018 --> 26:34.505
And all media, it will be very difficult to separate deep fake from reality.

26:35.246 --> 26:40.555
To escape the judgment reserved for a God-rejecting world, we must know Jesus as Lord and Savior.

26:41.496 --> 26:53.255
If you have not done so, I'm inviting you to call in His name and believe that He is the Son of God who died for our sins and rose from the dead, and the Bible promises you shall be saved.

26:53.916 --> 26:57.682
So no matter how chaotic and dangerous the world is becoming, the question is,

26:57.954 --> 27:00.778
Are we really ready for the soon-sudden appearing of the Lord?

27:01.399 --> 27:05.765
The Bible says, believe in the Lord Jesus Messiah, and you will be saved.

27:05.946 --> 27:06.306
Amen.

27:07.348 --> 27:13.016
Meanwhile, we'd love to hear from you on social media or through our free Jerusalem channel, Mobile App.

27:13.036 --> 27:25.394
Please follow my articles at substack.com and all of our videos at our Jerusalem channel, YouTube platform, as well as our website, exports.tv, where you have the opportunity to support our work financially.

27:26.050 --> 27:37.466
Finally, we invite you to sign up for our weekly email alert called exploits based upon Daniel 1132 declaring that people who know they're God will be strong not weak and will accomplish biblical exploits.

27:37.967 --> 27:41.532
The works of the Lord in the remaining time before His imminent return.

27:42.013 --> 27:45.057
You can sign up for that alert at our website.

27:45.738 --> 27:50.545
Meanwhile, let's keep contending for the faith and praying prophetically for the peace of Jerusalem.

27:50.885 --> 27:54.290
I'm Christine Darg, Shalom and Maranatha.

